title: Honor lv 4
body: Hey i got Honor lv 4 logging in today and i was wondering if anything special comes with it like exclusive to lv 4 honor. {{champion:203}}

replies.body: Honor level 4 means that you'll be able to display that shiny new Rank 4 loading screen flair, and you can find all of the other details on Honor Ranks over on our  [**Featured Honor Page**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/honor).
